title: Ep. 597 - Tapu Sena Cause Inconvenience To Bhide - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide is out in his living room relaxing as he reads the newspaper, but soon after it comes to a halt when his peace gets disrupted by Tapu Sena's constant noise and tells them to keep quiet!

title: Ep. 598 - Jetha Is Furious With Sodhi - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha gets super upset with the fact that Daya snitched on him to Sodhi and keeps complaining day and night about how Sodhi always listens to his wife and that Jetha doesn't do much nowadays.

title: Ep. 599 - A Party At Sodhi's - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sodhi is out partying with his friends but hasn't informed his wife about it. Roshan starts to get worried about the fact that it's midnight and Sodhi hasn't arrived yet. Did Sodhi encounter any mishap? Watch to find out!

title: Ep. 600 - Roshan Asks Bhide For Help - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide, Popatlal and Mr. Iyer look for Sodhi. Unable to find him, they spend the whole night sleeping there. Later, they helped Sodhi come back home.

title: Ep. 601 - Sodhi Is Unwell - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sodhi has to take the children to the resort. Due to the intoxication of alcohol last night, he is unwell. Roshan takes Sodhi to Dr. Haathi. Sodhi reveals to Bhide that he had gulped a piece of glass.

title: Ep. 602 - Sodhi Needs An Operation - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Haathi asks Sodhi for an XRay. Dr. asks him to get the operation done soon. Sodhi decides to reveal the truth to Roshan.

title: Ep. 603 - Gathering At The Hospital - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone comes to know that Sodhi has to undergo an operation. Roshan fights with Sodhi as she was lied to. Sodhi apologizes to Roshan and refuses to undergo operation unless she forgives him.

title: Ep. 604 - Roshan Reveals The Truth - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone reveals the truth that they made a fool out of Sodhi. Roshan narrates how she got to know the truth and hence made the plan to teach him a lesson. Daya makes fun of Jethalal.

title: Ep. 605 - Bhide Wants A Phone - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya shows a photo of Jethalal eating mango spilled over his face and shirt to Babita and Mr. Iyer. Bhide visits Jethalal's shop to get a low budget phone.

title: Ep. 606 - The Mango Season - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The ladies decide not to buy mangoes as it is huge priced. Jethalal could not get mangoes for Tapu. Bhide is angry with Jethalal.

title: Ep. 607 - Jethalal And Bhide Get Into A Fight - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide gets another phone from Jethalal. Jethalal narrates the whole story to all others where they get into a fight. Bhide wants to start a mango business.

title: Ep. 608 - Bhide Starts A Business - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Madhvi and Bhide visit everyone's home to take order for mangoes. Along with the mangoes, Madhvi has a scheme for it. They order mangoes from Ratnagiri.

title: Ep. 609 - The Mango Stall - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: A stall is set up in Gokuldham where Bhide and Madhvi will take order for mangoes. Finally, a truck full of mangoes come and Bhide starts distributing it. Bhide decides to personally go and give mangoes to Jethalal.

title: Ep. 610 - The Love For Mangoes - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone in Gokuldham is happy with the mango delivery. Daya decides to share some mangoes with Sundar and her mother. Later, Daya finds all the mangoes to be rotten.

title: Ep. 611 - Mango Business Goes Wrong - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After Daya, everyone else finds the mangoes to be rotten and go to Bhide to let him know about the quality of mango. Jethalal is furious with Bhide.
